    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The practice of seaborne looting via private armed vessels holding a government commission known as a letter of marque that authorizes the capture of merchant shipping belonging to an enemy nation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
